ipmsState.name: ipmsState
ipmsState.description: The current state of IPMS. When read this flag indicates whether IPMS is enabled or disabled. Setting this flag to enabled causes the IPMS software to be loaded. Setting this flag to disabled causes the IPMS software to be unloaded. If this flag indicates that IPMS is disabled, then no other objects within the IPMS MIB can be accessed (because the IPMS software is not loaded on the switch). In other words, the full IPMS MIB is available only when this flag indicates that IPMS is enabled.

ipmsDIPAddressPortTable.name: ipmsDIPAddressPortTable
ipmsDIPAddressPortTable.description: This table contains entries that list which switch ports have requested membership in a specific IP Multicast Group. There are several slot/port combinations for each IP Multicast Group.

ipmsDIPAddressPortEntry.name: ipmsDIPAddressPortEntry
ipmsDIPAddressPortEntry.description: This defines an entry in the Destination IP Address/Port table.

ipmsDIPAddress.name: ipmsDIPAddress
ipmsDIPAddress.description: This field defines the Destination IP Multicast address for the fields that follow.

ipmsDIPDstVlan.name: ipmsDIPDstVlan

ipmsDIPDstVlanMask.name: ipmsDIPDstVlanMask
ipmsDIPDstVlanMask.description: This field contains the Vlan Mask for the afforementioned Vlan.

ipmsDIPSlotNumber.name: ipmsDIPSlotNumber
ipmsDIPSlotNumber.description: This field contains the slot number of the port that corresponds to the IP Multicast group that it has joined.

ipmsDIPPortNumber.name: ipmsDIPPortNumber
ipmsDIPPortNumber.description: This value contains the port number for this virtual port.

ipmsDIPPortType.name: ipmsDIPPortType

ipmsDIPPortInstance.name: ipmsDIPPortInstance

ipmsDIPPortService.name: ipmsDIPPortService

ipmsDIPSrcIPAddr.name: ipmsDIPSrcIPAddr
ipmsDIPSrcIPAddr.description: This value contains the IP address of the station sending the membership report.

ipmsDIPPortTimeout.name: ipmsDIPPortTimeout
ipmsDIPPortTimeout.description: This value contains the timeout value in seconds for this port.

ipmsNbrVlanID.name: ipmsNbrVlanID

ipmsNbrVlanMask.name: ipmsNbrVlanMask
ipmsNbrVlanMask.description: This field contains the Vlan Mask of the neighboring router.

ipmsNbrSIPAddress.name: ipmsNbrSIPAddress
ipmsNbrSIPAddress.description: This field defines the IP address of the neighboring router.

ipmsNbrSlotNumber.description: This field contains the slot number of the neighboring router.

ipmsNbrPortNumber.name: ipmsNbrPortNumber

ipmsNbrPortService.description: This value contains the service of the neighboring router.

ipmsNbrPortTimeout.name: ipmsNbrPortTimeout
ipmsNbrPortTimeout.description: This value contains the timeout value in seconds of the neighboring router.

ipmsStatsTable.name: ipmsStatsTable
ipmsStatsTable.description: This table contains entries that supply statistical information about the IP Multicast traffic that is being switched and forwarded by this router.

ipmsStatsEntry.name: ipmsStatsEntry
ipmsStatsEntry.description: This table entry describes the entries included in the above tables.

ipmsStatsDIPAddress.name: ipmsStatsDIPAddress
ipmsStatsDIPAddress.description: This field contains the Destinatin IP address of the dest/source entry value. There can be many IP source addresses for a given Destination IP address.

ipmsStatsSIPAddress.name: ipmsStatsSIPAddress
ipmsStatsSIPAddress.description: This field contains the Source IP Address for a given Destination IP address.

ipmsStatsVlanID.name: ipmsStatsVlanID

ipmsStatsPacketsOut.name: ipmsStatsPacketsOut
ipmsStatsPacketsOut.description: This field contains the number of packets that have been sent for a given Destination IP/source IP address pair.

ipmsStatsSecsSinceZeroed.name: ipmsStatsSecsSinceZeroed

ipmsStatsAveragePPS.name: ipmsStatsAveragePPS
ipmsStatsAveragePPS.description: This field contains the average number of packets per second for this data flow.

ipmsZeroStatsFlag.name: ipmsZeroStatsFlag
ipmsZeroStatsFlag.description: Seting this flag to one causes statistics counters to be zeroed.

ipmsForwardingTable.name: ipmsForwardingTable
ipmsForwardingTable.description: This table contains entries that represent the contents of IPMS forwarding table. For each source and destination IP address pair, several slot/port combinations can be assigned.

ipmsFwdDstSlotNumber.name: ipmsFwdDstSlotNumber
ipmsFwdDstSlotNumber.description: This field contains the slot number of the svpn that has requested the multicast stream.
